{"tid":1006262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣兩隻貓墮樓 一重傷一逃去","createTime":"2019-02-02T23:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T09:49:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cff8c02e0752c59f36b48e7a7f4e495f1f2700ba","tid":1006262,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T23:01:27.000Z","msg":"荃灣沙嘴道131號一幢七層高唐樓，清晨近5時，一名男途人經過聽到嘭嘭兩聲巨響，發現兩隻貓由高處墮下，跌在馬邊旁邊，其中一隻一拐一拐沿唐樓梯級返回樓上，另一隻腹部受傷流血及腳部骨折，倒卧地上。<br />\n<br />\n男途人隨即報警，以及到對面大廈獸醫診所求救，但診所未有開門。受傷貓隻由途人移往行人路，警方通知愛護動物協會人員到場，將受傷貓隻撿走，逃走一隻則未有尋回。警方調查相信事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190203/59218124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59218124&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=07af2ffe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59218124&h=7f03a097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190203/59218124</a>"},{"pid":"40f53180c0db08772664756fe5e2a88ad789234a","tid":1006262,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T23:04:25.000Z","msg":"沒可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ac501e457716d518d070622efc41651be93a73","tid":1006262,"uid":43041,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T23:05:51.000Z","msg":"求助網站和熱線<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線 : 23892222<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線 : 24667350<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線︰28960000<br />\n<br />\n​學友社學生熱線：25033399<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線 : 23820000"},{"pid":"d264975acb0e9ff7977f7f757e3318a314b670a9","tid":1006262,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T23:13:18.000Z","msg":"一重傷一逃去 <br />\n仲唔係貓幫打鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"h